f=Cybersecurity/warden/custom/security-exception-process/assets/exception-register-template.md · h1:Security Exception Register [business name]=Append-only. exception: compensating control hard expiry residual-risk owner. Expiry fails closed (reverts policy). Open-exception count risk signal. · h1:Security Exception Register [business name]=\| ID \| Policy/control excepted \| Reason \| Compensating control \| Expiry (hard) \| Residual risk (register ref) \| Owner \| Approval (warden-low / board-high) \| State \| · h1:Security Exception Register [business name]=\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\|---\| · h1:Security Exception Register [business name]=\| E-001 \| <FILL_IN> \| \| [required] \| [date] \| [R-ref] \| \| \| open / expired→reverted / renewed-[date] \| · h2:Signals=Open exception count: ___ (rising policy misfit discipline slip warden operator), Exceptions clustered one control: ___ revise policy, Any expired-but-not-reverted: **incident** (fail-closed breach)